import React, { useState } from "react"; import InputField from "./InputField"; import SelectField from "./SelectField"; import { educationOptions } from "../constants/form"; import Section from "./Section"; import { sendDetails } from "../api"; import { SchemaTypes } from "../utils"; const defaultForm = { email: "", fullName: "", age: "", education: "", institute: "", program: "", experience: "", canadaInstitute: "", canadaProgram: "", country: "", goals: "", scoresListening: "", scoresReading: "", scoresSpeaking: "", scoresWriting: "", isPaidTutionFees: null, paidTutionAmount: "", isGic: null, paidGicAmout: "", }; const schema = { email: SchemaTypes().string(), fullName: SchemaTypes().number(), age: SchemaTypes().number(), education: SchemaTypes().string(), institute: SchemaTypes().string(), program: SchemaTypes().string(), experience: SchemaTypes().string(), canadaInstitute: SchemaTypes().string(), canadaProgram: SchemaTypes().string(), country: SchemaTypes().string(), goals: SchemaTypes().string(), scoresListening: SchemaTypes().number(), scoresReading: SchemaTypes().number(), scoresSpeaking: SchemaTypes().number(), scoresWriting: SchemaTypes().number(), isPaidTutionFees: SchemaTypes().boolean(), paidTutionAmount: "", isGic: null, paidGicAmout: "", } export default function Form() { const [form, setForm] = useState(defaultForm); const handleChange = (value, name) => { setForm((prevState) => ({ ...prevState, [name]: value })); }; const handleSubmit = (e) => { e.preventDefault(); sendDetails(form); }; return (
